{{define "subject"}}You're in — welcome to GradConnect 🎉{{end}}

{{define "plainBody"}}
Hi {{.FirstName}},

Your email is verified and your GradConnect account is fully active. Welcome to the community.

Here's what you can do now:

1. Submit reviews
   Share your experience with graduate programmes — assessment styles, culture, compensation, progression. Your reviews help other graduates make informed decisions.

2. Edit as you learn
   Your views may change as you progress through a programme. You can update your reviews any time.

3. Explore with context
   Browse reviews filtered by your industry interests and location preferences.

A few things worth knowing:

- We take review integrity seriously. Be honest, be fair, and keep it constructive.
- Your personal details (including your email) are never shown alongside your reviews.
- Found a bug or have feedback? Reply to this email — we read every message.

Log in any time at https://gradconnect.com/login

Welcome aboard,
The GradConnect Team
{{end}}

